				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">At the moment, the only way to do it is to modify source code. At the end of the file &quot;includes/functions_bbas.php&quot;, find
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;return array_unique&#40;$ret&#41;;
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
and add before it:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;if &#40;! &#40;FALSE === strpos&#40;strtolower&#40;$text&#41;, 'www'&#41;&#41;&#41; &#123;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$ret&#91;&#93; = 'http&#58;//www/';
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
